ullam is a 2012 tamil-language indian unreleased feature film directed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and produced by vedha , starring mithun and priyamani in the lead roles , while raghuvaran and karunas amongst others in supporting roles . the film has a music score composed by yuvan shankar raja , while suresh urs handled the editing of the venture . the film after production delays failed to gain a theatrical release and was released straight to dvd in 2012 . the film was premiered in sun tv on 1 june 2013 .